content:
Intent: Find Nearby Restaurants
ID: q3o4hi3q9034
Description: This intent is designed to help users find restaurants in their current location.  This only supports cities that are in the United States.  If the city is not within the United States, this intent should not be matched.
Slots:
    - Name: City
    ID: ka12jf193fjkasd
    Description: The name of the city to search the restaurant for
    Some examples: San Francisco, New York, Chicago

Intent: Order Food Online
ID: 109f313f09jkdfs03
Description: This intent enables users to place food orders online for delivery or pick-up.
Slots:
    - Name: Restaurant Name
      ID: 1234912fiw
      Description: Name of the restaurant to place food order
    - Name: Delivery or Pickup
      ID: 134fkl31fjj943
      Description: Whether the online order should be for delivery or pick-up
      Choose from following (must be one of these): delivery, pickup

Intent: Get Restaurant Menu
ID: 102943jfksd43
Description: This intent is for users who want to view a restaurant's menu before visiting or making an order.
Slots:
    - Name: Restaurant Name
      ID: 10239fjdsahf
      Description: The name of the restaurant to read the menu
    - Name: Meal
      ID: 12asdfkj349
      Description: Which meal menu to read
      Some examples: Breakfast, Lunch, Dinner, Dessert, etc.

Intent: Read Restaurant Reviews
ID: fdsjkfh0931skdf
Description: This intent helps users read reviews about a specific restaurant. 
Slots:
    - Name: Restaurant Name
      ID: 3294jfksdfj
      Description: The name of the restaurant to read reviews for

Intent: Make a Restaurant Reservation
ID: 2i4gj234g9r34
Description: This intent allows users to make reservations at their preferred restaurant.
Slots:
    - Name: Restaurant Name
      ID: 1304fj9kadsf
      Description: The name of the restaurant to make a reservation for
    - Name: Reservation Time
      ID: 34fjksdjf34
      Description: The time to make the reservation (must be between 10am and 6pm)
    - Name: Name of Reservation
      ID: dsfj934jo3fj
      Description: Name of the person that the reservation is under

Using the above schema, determine from the user utterance which intent or intents should be matched.  For each intent matched, extract any associated slots if they exist.

Give your output in a JSON format where the key is "model output" and the value is a subdictionary.  This subdictionary should have keys associated to the ID of each matched intent and the value should be another subdictionary.  The keys for this subdictionary should be each slot ID associated with the intent and the value should be the extracted slot value.  If there are no intent matched, return an empty subdictionary.  If there are a slot does not exist in the utterance, put "NA" as the value.

Here's an example format
{
    "model output": {
        "intent_id": {
              "slot_id1": "slot_value1",
              "slot_id2": "slot_value2"
        }
    }
}

This is the utterance from the user:

How much wood could a wood chuck chuck if a wood chuck could chuck wood
